## Agent Layer Detail

### Agent Default Configuration
All agents inherit from `agents.defaults`:
- Primary model: `ollama/glm-5:cloud`
- Fallback: `openrouter/google/gemini-2.5-flash-lite`
- Default workspace: `/Users/david/.openclaw/workspace-main`
- Bootstrap max chars: 250,000 (total: 300,000)
- Context tokens: 48,000
- Memory search: `nomic-embed-text` via local Ollama at `127.0.0.1:11434`, SQLite vector store
- Compaction: safeguard mode, reserve 18k tokens, keep 6k recent, max 60% history share
- Max concurrent agents: 4 (subagents: 8)
- Session timeout: 300s

