### Workspace Structure
Each workspace contains identity and behavioral files loaded at session start:
- `SOUL.md` — agent personality and purpose
- `IDENTITY.md` — role, responsibilities, what the agent does and does not do
- `AGENTS.md` — operating model: startup procedure, trust model, execution defaults, tool rules
- `HEARTBEAT.md` — behavior during periodic heartbeat runs
- `MEMORY.md` — digest/router pointing to canonical memory files
- `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` — daily working notes
- `agents/<role>/` — per-sub-role behavioral docs (BEHAVIOR.md, GUARDRAILS.md, DECISION_FRAMEWORK.md, etc.)

